36:25.417 --> 36:30.388 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This week, the National Oceanic
and Atmospheric
Administration released a new
decade-long

36:30.422 --> 36:34.793 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
plan to try to deal with the way
it's affecting
life underwater.

36:34.826 --> 36:37.395 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Special correspondent Cat Wise
has our report.

36:37.429 --> 36:41.699 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
