covering the
Leading Edge of science and
technology.

36:41.733 --> 36:47.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: Beachgoers are drawn
to the water
this time of year to relax and
enjoy some

36:47.439 --> 36:48.973 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
