36:59.717 --> 37:04.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CAT WISE: But the calm near the
surface often
belies what it actually sounds
like deep beneath

37:04.622 --> 37:14.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
