environments has
increased.

37:28.546 --> 37:33.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But many species of mammals,
fish, and even
invertebrates rely on sound to
communicate

37:33.251 --> 37:36.688 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
