waters, especially
around container ships.

38:18.930 --> 38:28.039 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARLA HOLT: OK, so here are orca
calls with
minimal boat noise.

38:28.072 --> 38:34.579 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
