when it comes
to driving foundation piles in
the water.

39:36.808 --> 39:40.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RHONDA BROOKS: I think it's only
really been
in the last decade or so that we
have become

39:40.245 --> 39:47.518 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
