sometimes
not very much, as little as 30
percent.

40:27.025 --> 40:29.827 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They also can cause construction
delays, according
to Brooks.

40:29.861 --> 40:32.430 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RHONDA BROOKS: As we know, time
is money in
construction.

40:32.463 --> 40:36.134 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so we began to look at
practical, innovative
ways to attenuate that sound.

40:36.167 --> 40:40.338 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
