Washington: Once
we understood the principles of
how sound

40:47.979 --> 40:51.449 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
was created, then the solution
was pretty
simple.

40:51.482 --> 40:55.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
