marine construction,
and what he came up with was a
double-walled

41:07.332 --> 41:08.399 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
pile.

41:08.433 --> 41:10.802 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Reinhall showed me how the
system works on
a model.

41:10.835 --> 41:16.774 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PER REINHALL: So, what we have
done is, we
have taken the ordinary pile and
then we have

41:16.808 --> 41:18.943 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
