there's an airspace
in between where the water can
not get to.

41:25.216 --> 41:29.020 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And what we do is, we strike the
inside pile.

41:29.053 --> 41:30.421 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
