we're coming
back to society.

45:30.962 --> 45:37.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we're trying to come back
prepared to
be citizens, and give back to
where we took

45:37.668 --> 45:39.570 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
