Coast Guard
life station in the entire
country.

50:42.106 --> 50:47.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It is located on Little Brewster
Island at
the entrance of Boston Harbor.

50:47.711 --> 50:53.651 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
